lead_paragraph: Former champion Bubba Watson birdied three of the last eight holes, and conjured a brilliant up-and-down on 18, to edge one stroke clear of a congested leaderboard in the Northern Trust Open third round on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Magical Watson Moves One Ahead at Sunny Riviera
